LARDD 1
TITLE lardos-arm-mobile
TEXT LardOS for ARM phones and tablets.
SECTION Identity
ITEM Branch: lardos-arm-mobile
ITEM Version line: v3.0.0b-lardos-arm-mobile
ITEM Channel: beta source/port branch
ITEM Architecture target: ARM/AArch64 mobile
SECTION Current State
ITEM The existing bootable OS media path is x86 BIOS/long-mode.
ITEM This branch does not call x86 ISO/IMG files ARM builds.
ITEM GitHub release is source-first until ARM boot media can be produced honestly.
SECTION Port Requirements
ITEM ARM entry code and exception vectors.
ITEM MMU/page table setup for ARM.
ITEM Timer and interrupt-controller support.
ITEM Mobile framebuffer/display and touch/input drivers.
ITEM Storage path suitable for phone/tablet flash media.
SECTION Values
ITEM User-owned settings, visible power policy, native formats, and local control stay mandatory.
ITEM Mobile convenience must never become hidden control by the OS.
END
